The percentages of cell viability of supercritical plants extract concentrations and anti-dengue data was analyzed by Microsoft Excel 2007 with the help of Tukey’s test (each treatment mean value different from each other and compared to control). The results were expressed as mean ± standard deviations. The cell viability of plant was calculated as:
